dc_description_s: These polygon and point data layers represent PLSS for Wood County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Wood_PLSS_YE2016.gdb. The features included in this geodatabase are 'WOOD_PLSS_CONTROL_YE2016' and 'WOOD_PLSS_SECTIONS_YE2016'.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://opendata.woodcogis.com/
